SQL_STMT_U.val: select t2.clnt101_admno, t2.clnt102_clntno, t2.clnt110_name1,decimal(sum(t1.CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESMAN + t1.CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESAUTO),13,2) ,decimal(sum (CMON_TOTIFACTCOMMSCHED + CMON_TOTIFACTCOMMSCHEDADD + CMON_TOTIMINCOMM + CMON_TOTIFIXCOMM),13,2), decimal(sum(t1.CMON_TOTIIFACTDEBIT + t1.CMON_TOTIIFACTSURCHARGEOD + t1.CMON_TOTIIARRANGEM + t1.CMON_TOTIISTOCK),13,2) from :1/cmon as t1, :1/clnt as t2 where clnt901_dateoperational>=':2' and clnt901_dateoperational<=':3' and clnt101_admno=cmon_admno and clnt102_clntno=cmon_clntno and cmon_currency='PLN' and cmon_year=:4 and cmon_month<=:5 and clnt101_admno=1 group by t2.clnt101_admno, t2.clnt102_clntno, t2.clnt110_name1 order by t2.clnt101_admno, t2.clnt102_clntno
